@startuml
title US-05: As a Patient, I want to search physicians by name or specialty.

actor Patient
participant PhysicianController
participant PhysicianService
participant PhysicianRepository
participant Physician

Patient -> PhysicianController : searchPhysicians(query)
PhysicianController -> PhysicianService : searchPhysicians(query)
alt search by name
    PhysicianService -> PhysicianRepository : findByNameContainingIgnoreCase(query)
else search by specialty
    PhysicianService -> PhysicianRepository : findBySpecialtyContainingIgnoreCase(query)
end
PhysicianRepository --> PhysicianService : List<Physician>
PhysicianService --> PhysicianController : List<PhysicianDTO>
PhysicianController --> Patient : 200 OK + List<PhysicianDTO>
@enduml